headline: Is Teledyne Still Attractive After Recent Aerospace and Defense Contract Wins?
summary: Wondering if Teledyne Technologies at around $502 a share is still worth buying, or if the easy money has already been made? You are not alone. This stock invites a closer look at what you are really paying for. Despite a soft patch recently, with the share price down 3.9% over the last week and roughly flat over the past month, Teledyne is still up 9.8% year to date and 8.1% over the last year, with multi year returns that quietly beat many industrial tech peers. headline: 3 Reasons to Sell TDY and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Teledyne has been treading water for the past six months, recording a small return of 2.8% while holding steady at $502.68. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 13.6% gain during that period.
